cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.GT, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with coordinating social ad campaigns over a social network, which falls under the category of social networks (cs.SI). The paper also uses submodular optimization techniques (cs.DS) and matroid constraints (cs.MA) to solve the optimization problem. The paper also discusses the Independent Cascade model (cs.GT) and LP rounding techniques (cs.AI) to obtain approximation algorithms.
